Package: paralleldice
Type: Package
Title: Calculate probabilities of various dice-rolling events
Version: 1.0
Date: 2015-03-20
Author: Nelson Johansen, Ricardo Matsui, Michael Polyakov 
Maintainer: Ricardo Matsui <rmmatsui@ucdavis.edu>
Description: This package parallelizes the dice package by Dylan Arena which provides utilities to calculate the probabilities of various dice-rolling events. The parallelizations are implemented using Snow, Thrust, and OpenMP.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.11.5)
Depends: R (>= 2.0.0), gtools, dice, ggplot2
LinkingTo: Rcpp
